# picrust
 
 - buy the parts, put a raspberry pi together
 - find an old laptop, install linux
 - set up apache and php
 - copy the replicator and run it
 - go to localhost
 - find ip address, put it in, replicate from localhost
 - set up links to folders, put images and media in them
 - connect with creators, get their media on thumb drives, paste in servers
 - take servers into venues, distribute media